&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Software Architect who fundamentally understands that software architecture is an economic and business tool, not just an academic exercise. We do not want an &quot;Ivory Tower&quot; architect who dictates policy from afar. Instead, we need a hands-on, pragmatic leader who operates as a &quot;civil servant&quot; to our execution teams, embedding with them to understand their daily friction and validating strategies through shared struggle. You will act as the technical North Star for the organization, driving major technical transitions, shaping our organizational design, and scaling the technical baseline of our entire engineering department.&lt;/p&gt;
