&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform Engineering Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide the creation of our internal developer platform, ensuring it is treated as a tier-one product rather than a ticketing desk. You will define the &quot;Thinnest Viable Platform&quot; to radically reduce developer cognitive load while maintaining team autonomy.&lt;/li&gt;
